&lt;p&gt;South Doc Services are looking for experienced bank HCAs to join our busy team to support us with a variety of services such as our new West Heath Drive Thru service which is due to open shortly at a Covid-19 red site based at West Heath Hospital, Rednal Road, Birmingham, West Midlands, B38 8HR and at our WiC at Katie Road in ?Selly Oak.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The hours of work will vary from Monday - Sunday.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candiate will have experience of working in primary care and an NVQ Level 2 in Health and Social Care or equivalent. You must also hold a certificate of complete in phlebotomy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have these skills and meet the requirements of the person specification attached we would like to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like more information please contact Jackie Heath on the number above.&lt;/p&gt;
